name: "Sabioshi Trio", three DIY designer papertoys, PDF printable / level: advanced
description: "Sabioshi Trio" is a set of three Designer Paper Toys by multitalented artist Marko Zubak, whose work has been published in various books and magazines around the globe. He has been active on the world Paper Toy scene since 2007. Building level: Advanced This work of art is in PDF format, so once your payment has gone through, I'll send you the files via e-mail. Most of my paper toys are for free and this is only symbolical support to my work. What you need: -Adobe Acrobat or PDF reader -Color Printer -Paper -Scissors -Ruler -Craft Knife -Glue -Surface to cut on FOR BEST RESULTS use photo matt paper, appropriate printing presets, craft knife and liquid glue for the paper. If you want to practice more, start your own Paper Toy collection, you can find more than 200 free Paper Toys on www.markozubak.com (or even join the artist in customization of his Paper Toys) Please let me know if you have any trouble!
